# Catch-all default — runs after the classify arms (scopes 100/110/120)
# have merged, so `@ticket.category == ""` is true only when none of
# them matched. It lives at its own later scope (150) rather than
# alongside the arms because a rule cannot see another rule's EMIT
# within the same scope.
WHEN @ticket.category == ""
  EMIT @ticket.category = "uncategorized",
       @ticket.priority = "low"
